  "body": "<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/microcontrollers\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"kofi-singular-alt\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/donate/kofi-singular-alt_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://codeberg.org/MicrocontrollersDev/NametagTweaks\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"codeberg\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/codeberg_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/nametag-tweaks\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector\" target=\"_blank\">\n  <img alt=\"sinytra connector\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/6j289t.svg\">\n</a>\n\n# Nametag Tweaks\n\nA small QOL mod that lets you change the look of nametags.\n\n## Features\n\n- Remove Nametags\n- Show Own Nametag\n- Hide Entity Nametags in F1 Mode\n- Hide Player Nametags in F1 Mode\n- Hide Armor Stand Nametags in F1 Mode\n- Nametag Height Offset\n- Custom Nametag Background Color\n- Nametag Text Shadow\n- Nametag Scale\n",
